            "text": "<p>1. Scope of application<br\/>2. Conclusion of contract<br\/>3. Right of withdrawal<br\/>4. Prices and terms of payment<br\/>5. Delivery and shipping conditions<br\/>6. Duration and termination of subscription contracts<br\/>7. Retention of title<br\/>8. Liability for defects (warranty)<br\/>9. Redemption of promotional vouchers<br\/>10. Applicable law<br\/>11. Place of jurisdiction<br\/>12. Code of Conduct<br\/>13. Alternative Dispute Resolution<br\/>14. Scope<\/p>",
