          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>3.1 Consumers are generally entitled to a right of withdrawal. Further information on the right of withdrawal can be found in the Seller's instructions on withdrawal.<br\/>3.2 The right of withdrawal does not apply to consumers who do not belong to a Member State of the European Union at the time of conclusion of the contract and whose sole place of residence and delivery address are outside the European Union at the time of conclusion of the contract.<\/p>",
            "text_size_mobile": "16px",
